  <summary date="2022-04-08T19:58:41Z" status="Introduced in House">JAB Act or the Justice for All Businesses Act

This bill restricts the Department of Labor from engaging in rulemaking to require that employers mandate COVID-19 vaccination or testing of employees.

Specifically, Labor may not use any funds to draft, promulgate, or enforce such a rule. Additionally, Labor may not assess civil monetary or criminal penalties for violations.</summary>
